[media] dw2102: switch ts2022 to ts2020 driver

Change ts2022 driver to ts2020 driver. ts2020 driver supports
both tuner chip models.

That affects TechnoTrend TT-connect S2-4600 DVB-S/S2 device, which
Olli just added.

